ground_truth:
program Cake 
kamus : 
    N, d, t : integer
    Lpl, Kpl, satC, potC : real
Algoritma  
    input (N, d, t)
    Lpl <- (3.14 * ((d div 2) + (d div 2) * t) 
    Kpl <- ((4 * 3.14) * (d div 2) + (d*N))
    potC <- ((d div 2) * (d div 2)) * (3.14 div N)
    SatC <- Lpl + Kpl - potC
    output (satC)
endprogram
